\begin{frame}{Connected Sum: g Tori}

What is the Euler characteristic of $T_N = T_1 \# T_1 \# \hdots \# T_1$ g times?

\uncover<2->{

\[ \chi = 2 - 2g \]


}

\uncover<3->{
\begin{itemize}[label=$\blacktriangleright$]

    \item $g$ is known as the ``genus''

\end{itemize}
}

\end{frame}

